 PromptuKit
 ==========
 Utilities for building and managing multiple-choice question banks and generating exam PDFs.
+
+### MATLAB interoperability example
+
+The repository includes an optional MATLAB interoperability example in
+[`examples/matlab`](examples/matlab). It demonstrates a simple pattern where
+MATLAB computes or stores numerical results, calls a Python script with
+`pyrunfile`, and the Python side uses PromptuKit's question-model and validation
+utilities to generate a structured calculation question bank.
+
+MATLAB is not a PromptuKit dependency; this example is documentation-focused and
+can be smoke-tested from Python without MATLAB.
 
 Install from PyPI
